Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This building is located in a campus setting with easy access to The Greater Pittsburgh International Airport, the Parkway West, Route 60 and I-79.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Cherrington Corporate Center was completed in 1997 and features seven buildings with a total of 454,890 square feet. Conveniently located in Moon Township, Cherrington Corporate Center is the closest suburban office park to the Pittsburgh International Airport. The center is under new, institutional-quality ownership that will be invigorating the park with best-in-class amenities and renovations. These additions and renovations will enhance Cherrington Corporate Centerâ€™s position as the principal office park near the airport.

Cherrington Corporate Center offers excellent access to Business Loop 376 and Beaver Grade Road. With a variety of buildings and floor plates, the center can accommodate tenants of all sizes. Cherrington Corporate Center provides perks and programs befitting that of a modern-day office complex, including state-of-the-art amenities such as event, conference, and training centers, tenant lounges, food hall and community space.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Cherrington Corporate Center is the premier choice for corporate tenants who desire suburban office space near the airport with free parking and best-in-class amenities.
